root.go Root command configuration
Sets up the main treex command with flags and subcommand delegation

show.go Default tree display command
Implements the main tree visualization functionality with formatting options

add_info.go Interactive command to **add** or *update* entries in `info` files

init.go Initialize .info files
Creates new .info files with optional path entries

check.go Validate .info files
Checks .info files for syntax errors and missing paths

gen_info.go Generate .info from tree text
Creates .info files from tree-like text input

make_tree.go Create directory structures
Builds file system structures from tree representations

make_tree_test.go Tests for make-tree command

info_files.go Documentation command
Shows detailed information about .info file format

templates/ Template files
Contains embedded templates for generating documentation
